keyMappings:
unmapAll

map <c-n> scrollDown
map <c-p> scrollUp
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map r reload
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map ;t LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map <c-b> goBack
map <c-f> goForward
map <c-j> nextTab
map <c-k> previousTab
map dd removeTab
map [ goPrevious
map ] goNext
